description:
For our February talk night Tim Condon (one of the authors of Server Side Swift with Vapor https://store.raywenderlich.com/products/server-side-swift-with-vapor ) has kindly offered to come speak about Server Side Swift. More speakers to be announced soon...

Tim Condon - Full Stack Development with Swift
Eddy Gammon - A11Y Is For Everyone
Matt Hamilton - Introduction to AI / Machine Learning

We're also looking for another speaker, so if you fancy dusting off that talk you've thought about giving just get in touch with one of the organisers (first time talks are very welcome).

Location - Dyson’s Bristol office
title: Server Side Swift and more! Feb Talk Night
